		<title>04INDUSTRY TRADE WORK</title>
		<content> Shotts contains the following:        
                                       
 A brickworks               :closed    
 Bluebell knitwear factory  :closed    
 Tempo Toys                 :closed    
 A sawmill                             
 Camp's Icecream factory               
 Mmumms food processors                
 Safeline protective clothing          
 Bell's Bakery                         
 Repetition toolmakers                 
 Other employers are:                  
   Hartwood Hospital                   
   Shotts Prison                       
   Ambulance service                   
   Local government, shops etc.        
                  The present rate of  
 unemployment is well in excess of 10% 
   The closure of the coalmines has    
 contributed to this.                  
                                       
                                       </content>
